quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  35,4,aur ( ae paighambar ) agar yeh log tum koj hutla-ayn to tum se pehlay bhi paighambar jhutlaye gay-ay hain. aur ( sab ) kaam khuda hi ki taraf lout’tay jayen ge
  35,5,logo khuda ka wada sacha hai. to tum ko duniya ki zindagi dhokay mein nah daal day aur nah ( shetan ) fraib dainay wala tumhe fraib day
  35,6,shetan tumhara dushman hai tum bhi usay dushman hi samjhoo. woh apne ( پیروؤں ke ) giroh ko bulaataa hai taakay dozakh walon mein hon
  35,7,j_hnon ne kufarkiya un ke liye sakht azaab hai. aur jo imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay un ke liye bakhshish aur bara sawab hai
  35,8,bhala jis shakhs ko is ke aamaal bad aaraasta karkay dukhaay jayen aur woh un ko umdah samajhney lagey to (kiya woh nekokaar aadmi jaissa ho sakta hai ). be shak khuda jis ko chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jis ko chahta hai hadaayat deta hai. to un logon par afsos karkay tumhara dam nah nikal jaye. yeh jo kuch karte hain khuda is se waaqif hai
  35,9,aur khuda hi to hai jo hawae chalata hai aur woh baadal ko abharti hain phir hum un ko aik be jaan shehar ki taraf chillate hain. phir is se zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah kardete hain. isi terhan mardon ko jee uthna hoga
  35,10,jo shakhs izzat ka talab gaar hai to izzat to sab khuda hi ki hai. isi ki taraf pakeeza kalmaat charhtay hain aur naik amal is ko buland karte hain. aur jo log buray buray makr karte hain un ke liye sakht azaab hai. aur un ka makr nabood hojaye ga
  35,11,aur khuda hi ne tum ko matti se pedakiya phir nutfay se phir tum ko jora jora bana diya. aur koi aurat nah haamla hoti hai aur nah janati hai magar is ke ilm se. aur nah kisi barri Umar walay ko Umar ziyada di jati hai aur nah is ki Umar kam ki jati hai magar ( sab kuch ) kitaab mein ( likha howa ) hai. be shak yeh khuda ko aasaan hai
